data.description: Beautiful single story home offering 3 bedrooms, two full baths and two car garage in the sought after neighborhood of Rivercrest.  Fresh landscaping welcomes you as you walk up to the front door. Once in the foyer, you will immediately notice the gorgeous flooring and open concept.  The main living area is spacious and light filled.  The kitchen features a breakfast bar, plenty of cabinet space and has enough room for an island, if desired.  The sizeable master bedroom offers a walk in closet, a shower and tub in the master bath along with a nice size linen closet.  Enjoy this incredible Florida weather by spending time in the oversized screened lanai overlooking the tranquil pond.    This well-maintained home has been professionally painted, inside and out, as well as a new HVAC (2016). With a low HOA, the Rivercrest community features an elementary school, Montessori school, daycare, 2 community pools and recreation center, tennis and basketball courts and mini-parks. Fantastic restaurants, grocery stores, big box stores and shopping are minutes away.  Conveniently located with easy access to I-75 and US-301. An easy commute to Tampa International Airport, MacDill AFB and downtown. Only 30 minutes to world class sandy beaches, and 90 minutes to Disney. Be in the home you love with the space you need in the neighborhood you deserve. Call to schedule your private tour today!
